title: CAKE in Binance Launchpad
body:
**Get in the context:**

For the ones who doesn't know what's Binance Launchpad, it's a Binance platform designed for launching & farming new tokens.

Recently, the Mobox team allocated 3 million of their native tokens to be farmed by Binance users for a small period of time. Among this movement, Binance listed their token in several pairs. As consequence from the launchpad offering and the listing, MBOX gained a 150% in less than 4 hours.

PancakeSwap team are great friends with Binance, but there has never been such an event in their launchpad platform, yet.

**The proposal:**

**Allocate 800,000 CAKE tokens** *(~16 M $USD)* substracted from the weekly burn to be launched on Binance Launchpad.

This will allow all Binance's users to farm CAKE tokens with BNB, BUSD and CAKE. It can't be a better marketing campaign than appear in the first page of Binance, seen by millions of users, to increase the CAKE adoption and keep building its real value.

Give yourself a while to think about it and take your own conclusions, then leave your vote here. Remember, this is a community proposal, it needs visibility (a lot of votes) to be seen by the chefs and so they can make it a reality.
*#Cake4Ever*
